{
  "name": "Light Step Mastery",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-orange.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Taijutsu </p><p>You've mastered the art of fighting while minimally armored, treating combat as an elegant dance.</p><p> While you are wearing no armor, you gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Whenever an attack roll misses you, you may move 5 feet without triggering attacks of opportunity.</p><p>• Once per turn, when a creature misses you with an attack, your next attack against them deals an additional 1d8 damage.</p><p>• When you take the dash action, you may move an additional +10 feet.</p><p>• When a creature misses you with an attack, you gain a +1 bonus to your AC, up to a maximum of +2, until the beginning of your next turn.</p><p></p>",
